{
  "apps": [
    {
      "url": "https://github.com/frappe/frappe",
      "branch": "version-16"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://github.com/[ORG]/[APP_NAME]",
      "branch": "main"
    }
  ]
}
```

## Usage

1. Replace `[ORG]` and `[APP_NAME]`
2. Save as `apps.json` in frappe_docker root
3. Encode: `APPS_JSON_BASE64=$(base64 -w 0 apps.json)`
4. Build: `docker build --build-arg=APPS_JSON_BASE64=$APPS_JSON_BASE64 ...`

## Notes

- First entry is ALWAYS frappe
- Additional entries are your custom apps
- Branch should match production branch
- version-16 is current stable (2026)
